OL,3,CCommissioner denies blocking scrutiny
OL,4,Cover day centre closures
OL,6,FCaller, appointed to oversee #300
OL,7,Fmillion in budget cuts, recently
OL,8,Frejected calls from opposition
OL,9,Fcouncillors to reconsider the closures
OL,10,Famid strong opposition from service
OL,11,Fusers and their families.
OL,13,FReflecting on his role since last
OL,14,Fyear, Caller acknowledged the depth of
OL,15,Fthe council's financial difficulties,
OL,16,Fstating "This has been a very
OL,17,Fdifficult intervention ... I don't
OL,18,Fthink the council really appreciated
OL,19,Fhow far they had sunk in terms of
OL,20,Ftheir financial control".
