OL,6,FTasked with addressing Birmingham's
OL,7,Ffinancial crisis following the
OL,8,Fcouncil's declaration of effective
OL,9,Fbankruptcy, Caller emphasised that the
OL,10,Furgency of these decisions leaves
OL,11,Flittle room for delays.
OL,13,F"This is just one of the many
OL,14,Fdifficult decisions that the council
OL,15,Fhas to take"
OL,17,FHe explained his decision to block the
OL,18,Freconsideration of day centre
OL,19,Fclosures, citing three key reasons.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
