OL,3,CCommissioner denies blocking scrutiny
OL,4,Cover day centre closures
OL,6,F"First of all, when the council signed
OL,7,Fup for the exceptional financial
OL,8,Fsupport scheme, it undertook to
OL,9,Fgovernment that it would use the most
OL,10,Fexpeditious process to carry all the
OL,11,Fdifficult decisions ... This is just
OL,12,Fone of the many difficult decisions
OL,13,Fthat the council has to take, but it
OL,14,Fhas to do them at pace".
OL,16,FHe also noted that the decision had
OL,17,Falready undergone "pre-decision
OL,18,Fscrutiny," so revisiting it would only
OL,19,Fduplicate existing assessments.
