OL,6,FLastly, he added, "every month's delay
OL,7,Fcosts around #100,000, and that
OL,8,F#100,000 is other people's services,
OL,9,Fother jobs, other things that need to
OL,10,Fbe resolved".
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Conservative
OL,13,FGroup on the Council said:
