OL,3,CCommissioner denies blocking scrutiny
OL,4,Cover day centre closures
OL,6,FIn response to criticism from local
OL,7,Fleaders and residents, who feel
OL,8,Funelected officials may lack the
OL,9,Faccountability required for such
OL,10,Fimpactful decisions, Mr Caller
OL,11,Fdefended his approach.
OL,13,F"The council has got to move at pace.
OL,14,FIt's got to balance its books ...
OL,16,F"Every day that goes on when it
OL,17,Fcontinues to overspend puts more
OL,18,Fservices and more jobs at risk," he
OL,19,Fsaid, reiterating that his actions are
OL,20,Fguided by a commitment to stabilising
OL,21,Fthe council's finances.
