OL,6,FCaller also addressed concerns from
OL,7,Fservice users affected by the
OL,8,Fclosures, stating that while he
OL,9,Funderstands the impact, "This is not a
OL,10,Fcommissioner decision to promote the
OL,11,Fclosure of day centres... What the
OL,12,Fcommissioners are doing is ensuring
OL,13,Fthat when the council takes a decision
OL,14,Fin its budget that it delivers what it
OL,15,Fsays it's going to do".
